title: Justin Bieber, Big Narstie Get 'White Boy Wasted'
text: Justin Bieber, Big Narstie Get 'White Boy Wasted' Friday, 23 October 2015 (4 minutes ago) Instagram photo shows the pair hanging out... In what could be assumed to be a photoshop job, a new photo posted on *Big Narstie's* Instagram shows him and *Justin Bieber *hanging out. The grime legend has been known for his bromance with *Ed Sheeran*, and the snap shows the three of them posing side by side, with Narstie captioning: "Me ed Justin bieber I am white boy wasted riding my buzz tho BDL u cunts #base" Bieber replied, simply, with "base", referencing the MC colossus's catchphrase "don't fuck up the base".
